{"tid":1583643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】【人權法一秒文宣】美國參議員吹雞 要十萬Like同Retweet得唔得啊香港人？","createTime":"2019-09-20T16:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:36:54.000Z","uid":25178,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"42d4fdedfcc57773be9c44ec0f4756b5a8640f4d","tid":1583643,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署要打email打名又驗證又成都可以幾日就10萬聯署<br />\n而家美國參議員Marco Rubio吹雞睇下有幾多人支持「香港人權與民主法案」<br />\n冇理由唔表態啦?<br />\n<br />\n只需要喺Twitter撳「轉發(Retweet)」<br />\n簡單過白宮聯署 多你一個多好多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白宮聯署可以10萬 Twitter戰線都要有10萬得唔得?<br />\n你諗下<br />\nTrump喺twitter既post都係得幾千retweet<br />\n呢個吹雞post如果有10萬甚至更多<br />\n會make到好多noise<br />\n向世界展示香港民意<br />\n你都唔想畀葉劉有材料話香港只有小部分人撐人權法架？</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrubiopress/status/1174703441022783489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrubiopress%2Fstatus%2F1174703441022783489&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=8bb16516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrubiopress%2Fstatus%2F1174703441022783489&h=ae4a674c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrubiopress/status/1174703441022783489</a>"},{"pid":"0ed7cee7d87395d78bd1809e67b518d5b14b4b39","tid":1583643,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"6346fe03015ed861dd6cc584898d1b0e23a719a6","tid":1583643,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad760b0b2a2a97654956352ef1